gemma2.reason: Multiple pieces of text state that Centerville, Indiana observes Eastern Standard Time (EST) which is UTC-05:00 and during daylight savings time shifts to Eastern Daylight Time (EDT) which is UTC-04:00.  This clearly shows it's 5 hours behind UTC during EST and 4 hours behind UTC during EDT.
